### User Routes

### Get registration page
GET http://localhost:8080/user/register

### Register a new user
POST http://localhost:8080/user/register
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

username=newuser&email=newuser@example.com&password=securepassword

### Get login page
GET http://localhost:8080/user/login

### Login user
POST http://localhost:8080/user/login
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

username=existinguser&password=userpassword

### Logout user
GET http://localhost:8080/user/logout

### Get user details
GET http://localhost:8080/user/username

### Campaign Routes

### Get all campaigns
GET http://localhost:8080/campaigns

### Get campaign details
GET http://localhost:8080/campaigns/1

### Get campaign creation form
GET http://localhost:8080/campaigns/create

### Create a new campaign
POST http://localhost:8080/campaigns
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "New Campaign",
  "description": "Campaign description",
  "postal_code": "12345",
  "template": "Email template content"
}

### Delete a campaign
DELETE http://localhost:8080/campaigns/1

### Get campaign edit form
GET http://localhost:8080/campaigns/1/edit

### Update a campaign
PUT http://localhost:8080/campaigns/1
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

name=Updated Campaign&template=Updated template content

### Send a campaign
POST http://localhost:8080/campaigns/1/send
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

postal_code=12345&user_name=John Doe&user_email=john@example.com

### Representative Routes

### Lookup representatives
POST http://localhost:8080/representatives/lookup
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

postal_code=12345&type=MP

### API Routes

### Get all campaigns
GET http://localhost:8080/api/campaigns

### Get a specific campaign
GET http://localhost:8080/api/campaigns/1

